---

<FormatTemplate
  formatName="Capsule"
  heroTitle="Precision Capsule Manufacturing"
  heroDescription="Leverage pharmaceutical-grade encapsulation technology to power your supplement brand. Our diverse material options and advanced powder engineering ensure consistent dose delivery and maximum ingredient stability for clinical and retail success."
